                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14740802" author="pauloricardomg" created="Fri, 11 Sep 2015 13:34:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached patch. What happens here is that the node is shutdown before system keyspace flushing, so when the node is back, since token metadata is populated before commit log replay after &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-9317&quot; title=&quot;Populate TokenMetadata earlier during startup&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-9317&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-9317&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, the down peers which are loaded into system keyspace after commit log replay are not populated into token metadata until they&apos;re UP again.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Simple fix is to re-populate token metadata after commit log replay. Would you mind reviewing since it&apos;s related to #9317, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=krummas&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;krummas&quot;&gt;krummas&lt;/a&gt;?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This fix will most likely not affect anything afaic, but just in case, test results will appear shortly below:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://cassci.datastax.com/view/Dev/view/paulomotta/job/pauloricardomg-10293-3.0-dtest/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;3.0 dtests&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://cassci.datastax.com/view/Dev/view/paulomotta/job/pauloricardomg-10293-3.0-testall/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;3.0 testall&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://cassci.datastax.com/view/Dev/view/paulomotta/job/pauloricardomg-10293-trunk-dtest/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;trunk dtests&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://cassci.datastax.com/view/Dev/view/paulomotta/job/pauloricardomg-10293-trunk-testall/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;trunk testall&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14935335" author="jbellis" created="Tue, 29 Sep 2015 15:39:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Is this a problem in 2.2 or 2.1?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14935343" author="pauloricardomg" created="Tue, 29 Sep 2015 15:44:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Nope, only on 3.0.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14941089" author="carlyeks" created="Fri, 2 Oct 2015 12:53:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14946520" author="slebresne" created="Wed, 7 Oct 2015 08:44:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed, thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
